 </title><link>https://faq.i3wm.org/question/899/how-to-change-mod-key-to-control/?answer=900#post-id-900</link><description>Hi Kretortex,

this works for me

    bindsym Control+Left focus left

or

    set $mod Control

to change it troughout the file.</description><pubDate>Thu, 13 Dec 2012 20:11:16 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://faq.i3wm.org/question/899/how-to-change-mod-key-to-control/?answer=900#post-id-900</guid></item><item><title>Comment by Kelvin Hu for &lt;p&gt;Hi Kretortex,&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;this works for me&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;pre&gt;&lt;code&gt;bindsym Control+Left focus left
&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;

&lt;p&gt;or&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;pre&gt;&lt;code&gt;set $mod Control
&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;

&lt;p&gt;to change it troughout the file.&lt;/p&gt;
